{"tid":37223,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加暗示大肆增兵：一月我會好忙","createTime":"2016-12-13T08:31:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T09:09:20.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c268d1cfb5d49bcb6f93b028572e7a598f71356","tid":37223,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:31:55.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴領隊雲加表示，他希望在一月引入能增強球隊實力的球員，但他認為這是艱巨的任務。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴本季成績不佳，雲加也相信與球員實力有關，因此一向謹慎的他決定在一月收購球員。不過教授認為真正有質素的球員很難買到，而能夠買到的球員不一定能提升球隊實力。<br />\n<br />\n雲加接受採訪時說：「沒錯，一月我將很忙，我不會透露心儀球員的名字，你們媒體自己有辦法找到答案。我們有打入歐聯的實力，但我們也很希望增強實力，不過你很難在能夠購買的球員中，找到能提升我們實力的球員。沒錯，你希望找到能即買即用的球員，這就是困難的地方。雲佩斯雖然已經29歲，但曼聯花了2400萬鎊簽下他。」"},{"pid":"913b5216d6670f6ad093e6e246fc1a23946b2fa0","tid":37223,"uid":45487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:33:58.000Z","msg":"又險簽一隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2a1b025854ba2e630496e3e26fa332dded8529","tid":37223,"uid":20896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:38:48.000Z","msg":"今季成績真係差咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d79050c83770ff9f4b6cfc9c707125713c82f0","tid":37223,"uid":4469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:39:25.000Z","msg":"忙住點留奧燒同山神"},{"pid":"27804d8187e5dcfb9b8a4e69d0f0e140d74e3702","tid":37223,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:41:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今季成績真係差咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雲爺爺要突然歐聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a4d488f5d6897d960782870fc44fa2b6e78518e","tid":37223,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:41:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>今季成績真係差咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雲爺爺要突<span style=\"color: red;\">破</span>歐聯